d":93710,"uid":23296,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:53:49.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>More<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/08.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/10.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/01/25/004535_da209b409fe85b78d1745372aecc0b33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F01%2F25%2F004535_da209b409fe85b78d1745372aecc0b33.jpg&h=c204587a&s={SIZE}\" /></blockquote><br />\n幾靚仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4302973429438e534b9e65558a6134538c73b31f","tid":93710,"uid":8307,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T17:59:13.000Z","msg":"話說啱啱收工同個fd打羽毛球，<br />\n其實我一早有啲鍾意佢，今日特登打激啲出多啲汗等佢沖涼，又特登請佢飲野等佢去廁所個彈偷走佢枝沖涼水，等佢問我拎。<br />\n一開頭都係各有各沖，事情就同我想像既一樣，佢發現冇沖涼水問我借。<br />\n<br />\n咁等就話：「吓我帶嗰啲一包包旅行裝嚟咋喎，<br />\n你過埋嚟先啦，我睇吓點俾你。」<br />\n<br />\n我已經搽到成身鹼液，等佢行入黎。<br />\n之後我扭熄咗個水龍頭，<br />\n將個身拱埋去佢個身到輕輕咁頸貼頸身貼身咁磨。<br />\n<br />\n佢有啲喘氣咁問：「你&hellip;做乜撚&hellip;嘢&hellip;」<br />\n我笑咗一笑：「咁樣咪夠兩份人囉傻仔！」<br />\n<br />\n佢望住我，塊面都不自覺越來越紅，<br />\n我感覺到佢開始濕濕地，<br />\n我個lin頭又啱啱好頂住咗佢lin頭，<br />\n我輕輕咁un一un，<br />\n我地兩個條嘢就產生咗磨擦，<br />\n嗰種舒服嘅感覺係前所未有，<br />\n我真係唔識形容。<br />\n<br />\n佢見到我開始合埋眼enjoy緊呢個moment，<br />\n佢都好識趣咁慢慢輕咬我嘅嘴唇，<br />\n仲將佢條脷熟練咁滑入我口腔裡頭，<br />\n同我條脷互相交纏。<br />\n<br />\n到我地有咗共識，可以試吓俾我用手指插入佢到嘅時候<br />\n<br />\n突然洗廁所個呀婆一嘢拉開到簾，<br />\n佢尖叫道：「嘩！屌你兩個呀！該煨囉！」<br />\n<br />\n我地唯有尷尷尬尬咁即刻沖身走人，<br />\n而家個頭仲未洗，<br />\n屌！"},{"pid":"ea686c942f19713037a3ecb9ad672081db67dcab","tid":93710,"uid":23902,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:05:00.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\ngay test.."},{"pid":"6a9980750f643db7e7a55f60ec56d0811608cf94","tid":93710,"uid":15413,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:37:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>扯左</blockquote><br />\nx2"},{"pid":"ba151d120222902db02cb93acc6beb62dd1c7c08","tid":93710,"uid":36029,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:44:45.000Z","msg":"扯左，thx"},{"pid":"2e49fdd3175c710c484a59f11d38c2f815ea64eb","tid":93710,"uid":3189,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:54:14.000Z","msg":"扯左<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7727aff9187d4c22195cbf881568ef96778bbfe2","tid":93710,"uid":15129,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T18:58:26.000Z","msg":"試過 不過唔會得冲涼咁單純<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8452cb1f431d83d80d515562e8d79a32d7342039","tid":93710,"uid":33159,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T22:16:31.000Z","msg":"上堂睇扯咗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b5afebf57fe88b226158f48fa731eb23ec18ca8","tid":93710,"uid":17510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:42:59.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/37.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cabf4166d03d61f996680ff595aa4d48b4dacad2","tid":93710,"uid":45772,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-24T23:50:22.000Z","msg":"笑死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img sr